+		/*
+		 * TODO: remove hack
+		 * Note: currently there is a bug in init_hw such that
+		 * on resume from hibernate, BIOS sets up MPCC0, and
+		 * we do mpcc_remove but the mpcc cannot go to idle
+		 * after remove. This cause us to pick mpcc1 here,
